T02D3671:284a-1: aarya t'a re de b'i sto tra n'a ma /
T02D3671:284a-3: 'phags ma lha mo sgrol ma la bstod pa zhes bya ba /
T02D3671:284a-4: rje btsun 'phags ma sgrol ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D3671:284a-5: bzlog dka' srid pa'i mun pa ni //
T02D3671:284a-7: thugs rjes brlan pa'i thugs mnga' ba //
T02D3671:284a-8: sgrol ma la ni rtag tu 'dud //
T02D3671:284a-9: shin tu rno ba'i sems rnams kyis //
T02D3671:284a-10: glang po che rnams gsol byed pa //
T02D3671:284a-11: lha mo seng ge khros pa yang //
T02D3671:284a-13: mche ba'i mdung rtse rnon po yis //
T02D3671:284a-15: khyod kyi sngags ni bzlas pa las //
T02D3671:284a-17: phyogs dang nam mkha' ma lus pa //
T02D3671:284a-18: du bas khyab cing bzod par dka' //
T02D3671:284a-19: 'bar ba yis ni khro tshig pa //
T02D3671:284a-20: khyod bstod char bas me zhir 'gyur //
T02D3671:284a-21: ma rungs gdengs ka las byung ba'i //
T02D3671:284a-22: phut sgra sgrogs shing dug mang can //
T02D3671:284a-23: sbrul ni lha mo khyod bstod pas //
T02D3671:284a-24: nam mkha' lding ni bzhin du 'jigs //
T02D3671:284a-25: ral gris gcod cing 'dral ba rnams //
T02D3671:284a-26: khrag gis yan lag bskus pa ste //
T02D3671:284b-0: khyod kyi ming tsam dran pa @284b yis ;
T02D3671:284b-1: / chom rkun nus pa med par 'gyur //
T02D3671:284b-2: rgyal po khros pas bran rnams kyi //
T02D3671:284b-3: skra nas bzung zhing zhags pas bcings //
T02D3671:284b-4: btson ra spangs te lha mo kye //
T02D3671:284b-6: dpa' rlabs tshogs kyis phyogs bcu dang //
T02D3671:284b-7: nam mkha' yang dag khyab byed pa //
T02D3671:284b-8: gru log na yang rgya mtsho las //
T02D3671:284b-9: khyod kyi 'phangs ni pha rol phyin //
T02D3671:284b-10: khrag dang klang pa'i 'dam gyis byugs //
T02D3671:284b-11: de dag bza' ba la chags pa //
T02D3671:284b-12: khyod la bstod pa tsam gyis ni //
T02D3671:284b-14: yan lag chad cing dri nga ba //
T02D3671:284b-15: khrag dang rang ni sna nas 'dzag / khyod la bstod pa tsam gyis ni //
T02D3671:284b-17: bkres skom gyis gdungs gces bu dang //
T02D3671:284b-18: slong ba yi dvags dang 'dra ba //
T02D3671:284b-19: khyod la bstod pa tsam gyis ni //
T02D3671:284b-22: de ltar sems nas khyod bstod pas //
T02D3671:284b-23: dge ba gang bsags de yis ni //
T02D3671:284b-24: 'jigs rten bde ba can thob shog /'phags ma sgrol
T02D3671:284b-25: ma'i bstod pa slob dpon chen po tsandra go mis
T02D3671:284b-28: // / seng ge glang chen me sbrul chom rkun dang //
T02D3671:284b-29: lcags sgrog chu dang sha za'i 'jigs pa ni //
T02D3671:284b-30: 'joms mdzad zla 'od phung po ltar 'dzin ma //
